    <item>
      <title>市场动荡之际，海洋世界推迟贷款再融资计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/seaworld-adds-to-postponed-term-loan-deals-amid-market-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球市场波动，海洋世界公园与娱乐公司推迟了 15.5 亿美元定期贷款的再融资计划，这是周一美国杠杆贷款市场的第二笔贷款再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/seaworld-adds-to-postponed-term-loan-deals-amid-market-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 20:02:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
